# HT Manager — Architecture Map

Full-stack TypeScript monorepo for managing a Hattrick football team. The server talks to the CHPP (Hattrick) API, persists data with Prisma/SQLite, and exposes a REST API. The React client consumes that API.

## Server (`server/src/`)

### Entry point

| File | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| `index.ts` | Boots Express, wires middleware, mounts routers, starts the cron scheduler, serves the production client build. |

### Routes — thin HTTP layer

| File | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| `routes/players.ts` | Express router for `/api/players`. Parses params, delegates to `player.service`, returns JSON. |
| `routes/marketStudies.ts` | Express router for `/api/market-studies`. Parses params, delegates to `marketStudy.service`, returns JSON. |
| `routes/priceModel.ts` | Express router for `/api/price-model`. Train model, get status, predict prices. Delegates to `pricePredictor.service`. |

### Services — business logic

| File | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| `services/player.service.ts` | Player CRUD, CHPP refresh, position-score computation, position-override persistence. |
| `services/marketStudy.service.ts` | Market study lifecycle: create, list, detail, search, bulk-update, resolve transfers. Also manages custom chart configs (create/delete). |
| `services/transferResolver.ts` | Matches pending transfer listings to completed transfers and resolves final prices/deadlines. |
| `services/soldPriceAggregator.ts` | Aggregates sold-player prices into chart-ready series (by age, by specialty). Custom charts use client-side aggregation instead. |
| `services/pricePredictor.service.ts` | Price prediction orchestration: trains OLS regression model from sold players, predicts prices for squad players, study players, or arbitrary skill sets. |

### CHPP integration

| File | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| `chpp/client.ts` | OAuth-signed HTTP client for the Hattrick CHPP API. Exposes typed methods (getPlayers, getPlayerDetails, searchTransfers, etc.). |
| `chpp/parsers.ts` | Transforms raw CHPP XML (parsed to JS objects) into typed domain shapes. Handles Stockholm-to-UTC date conversion. |
| `chpp/types.ts` | TypeScript interfaces for every CHPP response and sub-entity. |

### Lib — shared utilities

| File | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| `lib/asyncHandler.ts` | Wraps async Express handlers so rejected promises forward to the error middleware. |
| `lib/routeUtils.ts` | `parseIntParam` (safe param parsing) and `errorResponse` (consistent error JSON). |
| `lib/constants.ts` | Shared constants (`ONE_WEEK_MS`) and status enums (`TRANSFER_STATUS`, `MARKET_STUDY_STATUS`). |
| `lib/errorMiddleware.ts` | Global Express error handler — catches unhandled exceptions and returns a uniform error response. |
| `lib/positionRatings.ts` | HT position-skill weight coefficients; computes a 0–20 rating per position for a player. |
| `lib/regression.ts` | Pure-math OLS multivariate linear regression: feature extraction, training (normal equation), prediction. Used by `pricePredictor.service`. |

### Jobs

| File | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| `jobs/scheduler.ts` | Cron registry (`node-cron`). Registers and starts recurring background jobs. |

