## Client (`client/src/`)

### Entry & shell

| File | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| `main.tsx` | React root: mounts `QueryClientProvider`, `BrowserRouter`, and `<App />`. |
| `App.tsx` | Top-level layout (header, tab navigation) and route definitions. |

### Pages

| File | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| `pages/PlayersPage.tsx` | Lists squad players, triggers CHPP refresh. Uses React Query. |
| `pages/PlayerDetailPage.tsx` | Single-player view: skills, position ratings, position-override form. Uses React Query. |
| `pages/MarketStudiesPage.tsx` | Lists market studies, allows creating new ones. Uses React Query. |
| `pages/MarketStudyDetailPage.tsx` | Orchestrates study detail: metrics, filters, charts, results table. Delegates to sub-components and the `useMarketStudy` hook. |
| `pages/PriceModelPage.tsx` | Price prediction model management: view status, train/retrain the model. |

### Hooks

| File | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| `hooks/useMarketStudy.ts` | `useMarketStudyData` — fetches and caches a study, manages selected IDs and action handlers. `useStudyFilters` — filter/sort state for the results table. |
| `hooks/usePriceModel.ts` | React Query hooks for price model: `usePriceModelStatus` (status + train mutation), `usePlayerPrediction`, `useStudyPredictions`. |

### Components — market study

| File | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| `components/market-study/StudyMetrics.tsx` | Computed metrics cards (avg price, counts, etc.) for a study. |
| `components/market-study/StudyFilters.tsx` | Filter bar UI: status, age range, specialty dropdowns. |
| `components/market-study/StudyCharts.tsx` | Recharts visualisations: price-by-age and price-by-specialty. |
| `components/market-study/CustomChartBuilder.tsx` | Form for adding a user-defined custom chart (group-by dimension + optional filters). |
| `components/market-study/CustomChart.tsx` | Renders a single custom bar chart; aggregates sold-player data client-side via `chartAggregator`. |
| `components/market-study/StudyResultsTable.tsx` | Sortable, filterable table of study transfer results with row selection. |

### Components — shared / domain

| File | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| `components/PlayerCard.tsx` | Compact player summary card (name, age, skills, TSI). |
| `components/PlayerList.tsx` | Renders a list of `PlayerCard` items. |
| `components/PlayerAvatar.tsx` | Composites Hattrick avatar layers into a single image. |
| `components/SkillBar.tsx` | Horizontal bar showing a skill level with colour coding. |
| `components/PositionRatingsCard.tsx` | Grid of position ratings with weighted-skill breakdowns. |
| `components/TransferResultCard.tsx` | Card displaying a single transfer search result with skills. |
| `components/MarketStudyForm.tsx` | Form for creating a new market study (skill type, min/max, age). |

### Components — UI primitives

| File | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| `components/ui/LoadingSpinner.tsx` | Reusable full-width loading spinner. |
| `components/ui/ErrorAlert.tsx` | Reusable red error alert box. |
| `components/ui/ActionMessage.tsx` | Feedback message for user actions (info or error variant). |
| `components/ui/BackLink.tsx` | "← Back" navigation link. |

### Lib — client utilities

| File | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| `lib/api.ts` | Typed API client: `fetchJson`/`postJson`/`patchJson`/`deleteJson` wrappers over `fetch`. One function per endpoint. |
| `lib/types.ts` | Shared TypeScript interfaces for API responses and domain models (`Player`, `MarketStudy`, `TransferSearchResult`, etc.). |
| `lib/skills.ts` | Skill-level labels, colour mapping, and skill-key metadata for the HT skill system. |
| `lib/skillTypes.ts` | `SKILL_TYPE_MAP`, `SKILL_TYPE_LABELS`, `SKILL_TYPE_TO_FIELD` — single source of truth for CHPP skill-type IDs. |
| `lib/playerUtils.ts` | `displayName` and `hattrickPlayerUrl` — reusable player display helpers. |
| `lib/positionRatings.ts` | Position display metadata and weight definitions (client-side mirror of server ratings). |
| `lib/format.ts` | `formatNumber` and `formatMoney` — locale-aware number formatting. |
| `lib/chartAggregator.ts` | Client-side aggregation for custom charts: filters sold players, groups by a chosen dimension, computes avg price per bucket. |
| `lib/priceModelApi.ts` | Typed API client for `/api/price-model` endpoints: train, status, predict for player/study/skills. |

